                                    oc:contentOrder 1 ;
                                    oc:textContent "**From Task 2's financial model, extract:**" ],
                                _:ref_de7bd80277910b6b ;
                            oc:sectionLevel 3 ;
                            oc:sectionOrder 6 ;
                            oc:sectionTitle "Step 1: Extract Data from Financial Model" ],
                        [ a oc:Section ;
                            oc:hasContent [ a oc:Paragraph ;
                                    oc:blockType "paragraph" ;
                                    oc:contentOrder 1 ;
                                    oc:textContent "**Note**: Only if M&A is relevant for this sector/company." ] ;
                            oc:hasSubsection [ a oc:Section ;
                                    oc:hasContent [ a oc:CodeExample ;
                                            oc:blockType "code_block" ;
                                            oc:codeContent """Target Company LTM EBITDA = $500M
Precedent Median EV/EBITDA (LTM) = 15.8x

Implied EV (Precedent) = $500M × 15.8x = $7,900M

Note: Precedent multiples typically 10-20% higher than trading comps
due to control premium and synergies.
""" ;
                                            oc:codeLanguage "" ;
                                            oc:contentOrder 1 ;
                                            oc:sourceLocation "lines 424-432" ] ;
                                    oc:sectionLevel 4 ;
                                    oc:sectionOrder 21 ;
                                    oc:sectionTitle "B. Apply to Target Company" ],
                                [ a oc:Section ;
                                    oc:hasContent [ a oc:CodeExample ;
                                            oc:blockType "code_block" ;
                                            oc:codeContent """PRECEDENT TRANSACTIONS ANALYSIS

Date     Target        Acquirer      Deal     EV/Rev  EV/EBITDA  Premium  Rationale
                                    Value($B)  LTM     LTM
Q1 2024  Comp A       Strategic      $5.2B    4.2x    16.5x      35%      Consolidation
Q3 2023  Comp B       PE Firm        $3.8B    3.8x    14.2x      28%      Platform
Q4 2023  Comp C       Strategic      $4.5B    4.0x    15.8x      32%      Geographic
Q2 2023  Comp D       Strategic      $6.1B    4.5x    17.2x      38%      Strategic fit
Q1 2023  Comp E       PE Firm        $3.2B    3.5x    13.5x      25%      Carve-out

Median                                        4.0x    15.8x      32%

Source: CapitalIQ, company filings, press releases.
""" ;
                                            oc:codeLanguage "" ;
                                            oc:contentOrder 4 ;
                                            oc:sourceLocation "lines 406-420" ],
                                        [ a oc:Paragraph ;
                                            oc:blockType "paragraph" ;
                                            oc:contentOrder 1 ;
                                            oc:textContent "**Search for 5-10 M&A deals:**" ],
                                        [ a oc:BulletList ;
                                            oc:blockType "bullet_list" ;
                                            oc:contentOrder 2 ;
                                            oc:hasItem [ a oc:BulletItem ;
                                                    oc:blockType "bullet_item" ;
                                                    oc:itemOrder 2 ;
                                                    oc:itemText "Similar size (0.5x to 2x target's size)" ],
                                                [ a oc:BulletItem ;
                                                    oc:blockType "bullet_item" ;
                                                    oc:itemOrder 3 ;
                                                    oc:itemText "Announced and closed deals" ],
                                                [ a oc:BulletItem ;
                                                    oc:blockType "bullet_item" ;
                                                    oc:itemOrder 1 ;
                                                    oc:itemText "Same industry, last 3-5 years" ] ],
                                        [ a oc:Paragraph ;
                                            oc:blockType "paragraph" ;
                                            oc:contentOrder 3 ;
                                            oc:textContent "**Example:**" ] ;
                                    oc:sectionLevel 4 ;
                                    oc:sectionOrder 20 ;
                                    oc:sectionTitle "A. Identify Relevant Transactions" ] ;
                            oc:sectionLevel 3 ;
                            oc:sectionOrder 19 ;
                            oc:sectionTitle "Step 4: Precedent Transactions (Optional)" ],
                        [ a oc:Section ;
                            oc:hasSubsection [ a oc:Section ;
                                    oc:hasContent [ a oc:CodeExample ;
                                            oc:blockType "code_block" ;
                                            oc:codeContent """PV of Projected FCF = Σ [FCFt / (1 + WACC)^t] for t = 1 to 5

Example:
Year    FCF      Discount    PV of FCF
        ($M)     Factor      ($M)
2025    $250     1/(1.108)^1 = 0.9026    $226
2026    $320     1/(1.108)^2 = 0.8147    $261
2027    $390     1/(1.108)^3 = 0.7353    $287
2028    $450     1/(1.108)^4 = 0.6636    $299
2029    $500     1/(1.108)^5 = 0.5988    $299
                              Total PV:  $1,372M

PV of Terminal Value = Terminal Value / (1 + WACC)^5
PV of Terminal Value = $6,175M / (1.108)^5 = $6,175M × 0.5988 = $3,697M

Enterprise Value = $1,372M + $3,697M = $5,069M
""" ;
                                            oc:codeLanguage "" ;
                                            oc:contentOrder 1 ;
                                            oc:sourceLocation "lines 203-220" ] ;
                                    oc:sectionLevel 4 ;
                                    oc:sectionOrder 10 ;
                                    oc:sectionTitle "C. Discount Cash Flows to Present Value" ],
                                [ a oc:Section ;
                                    oc:hasContent [ a oc:Paragraph ;
                                            oc:blockType "paragraph" ;
                                            oc:contentOrder 7 ;
                                            oc:textContent "**4. Determine Capital Structure**" ],
                                        [ a oc:Paragraph ;
                                            oc:blockType "paragraph" ;
                                            oc:contentOrder 3 ;
                                            oc:textContent "**2. Determine Cost of Equity (CAPM)**" ],
                                        [ a oc:BulletList ;
                                            oc:blockType "bullet_list" ;
                                            oc:contentOrder 2 ;
                                            oc:hasItem [ a oc:BulletItem ;
                                                    oc:blockType "bullet_item" ;
                                                    oc:itemOrder 2 ;
                                                    oc:itemText "Example: 4.0-4.5% as of late 2024" ],
                                                [ a oc:BulletItem ;
                                                    oc:blockType "bullet_item" ;
                                                    oc:itemOrder 1 ;
                                                    oc:itemText "Use 10-year Treasury yield (check current rate)" ] ],
                                        [ a oc:CodeExample ;
                                            oc:blockType "code_block" ;
                                            oc:codeContent """Cost of Equity = Risk-Free Rate + Beta × Equity Risk Premium

Inputs:
- Risk-Free Rate: [Current 10-year Treasury, e.g., 4.2%]
- Beta: [Company beta from Bloomberg/FactSet or peer average]
- Equity Risk Premium: 5-6% (historical average)

Example:
Cost of Equity = 4.2% + 1.3 × 5.5% = 11.35%
""" ;
                                            oc:codeLanguage "" ;
                                            oc:contentOrder 4 ;
                                            oc:sourceLocation "lines 112-122" ],
                                        [ a oc:Paragraph ;
                                            oc:blockType "paragraph" ;
                                            oc:contentOrder 5 ;
                                            oc:textContent "**3. Determine Cost of Debt**" ],
                                        [ a oc:Paragraph ;
                                            oc:blockType "paragraph" ;
                                            oc:contentOrder 1 ;
                                            oc:textContent "**1. Determine Risk-Free Rate**" ],
                                        [ a oc:Paragraph ;
                                            oc:blockType "paragraph" ;
                                            oc:contentOrder 9 ;
                                            oc:textContent "**5. Calculate WACC**" ],
                                        [ a oc:CodeExample ;
                                            oc:blockType "code_block" ;
                                            oc:codeContent """WACC = (E/V × Cost of Equity) + (D/V × Cost of Debt × (1 - Tax Rate))

Example:
WACC = (90.9% × 11.35%) + (9.1% × 6.5% × (1 - 25%))
WACC = 10.32% + 0.44% = 10.76%

Round to: 10.8% for base case
""" ;
                                            oc:codeLanguage "" ;
                                            oc:contentOrder 10 ;
                                            oc:sourceLocation "lines 154-162" ],
                                        [ a oc:CodeExample ;
                                            oc:blockType "code_block" ;
                                            oc:codeContent """Use market values (not book values):

Market Value of Equity (E) = Share Price × Shares Outstanding
Market Value of Debt (D) = Total Debt (use book value if bonds not traded)
Total Value (V) = E + D

Weight of Equity = E / V
Weight of Debt = D / V

Example:
E = $5,000M (90.9%)
D = $500M (9.1%)
V = $5,500M (100%)
""" ;
                                            oc:codeLanguage "" ;
                                            oc:contentOrder 8 ;
                                            oc:sourceLocation "lines 137-151" ],
                                        [ a oc:CodeExample ;
                                            oc:blockType "code_block" ;
                                            oc:codeContent """Cost of Debt = Current borrowing rate or implied yield on bonds

For private companies:
Cost of Debt = Risk-Free Rate + Credit Spread (based on rating)

Example:
Cost of Debt (pre-tax) = 6.5%
Cost of Debt (after-tax) = 6.5% × (1 - 25% tax rate) = 4.875%
""" ;
                                            oc:codeLanguage "" ;
                                            oc:contentOrder 6 ;
                                            oc:sourceLocation "lines 125-134" ] ;
                                    oc:sectionLevel 4 ;
                                    oc:sectionOrder 8 ;
                                    oc:sectionTitle "A. Calculate WACC" ],
                                [ a oc:Section ;
                                    oc:hasContent [ a oc:Paragraph ;
                                            oc:blockType "paragraph" ;
                                            oc:contentOrder 4 ;
                                            oc:textContent "**Table 2: Revenue CAGR vs. Terminal EBITDA Margin**" ],
                                        [ a oc:Paragraph ;
                                            oc:blockType "paragraph" ;
                                            oc:contentOrder 1 ;
                                            oc:textContent "**Table 1: WACC vs. Terminal Growth Rate**" ],
                                        [ a oc:Paragraph ;
                                            oc:blockType "paragraph" ;
                                            oc:contentOrder 2 ;
                                            oc:textContent "Create 2-way sensitivity table:" ],
                                        [ a oc:CodeExample ;
                                            oc:blockType "code_block" ;
                                            oc:codeContent """Price Per Share ($)     Terminal EBITDA Margin (2029E)
Revenue CAGR    28%     30%     32%     34%     36%
15%             $38     $42     $46     $50     $54
20%             $42     $46     $51     $56     $61
25%             $46     $51     $56     $62     $68
30%             $51     $56     $62     $68     $75
35%             $56     $62     $68     $75     $83

Base Case: Rev CAGR = 25%, EBITDA Margin = 32% → $56
""" ;
                                            oc:codeLanguage "" ;
                                            oc:contentOrder 5 ;
                                            oc:sourceLocation "lines 261-271" ],
                                        [ a oc:CodeExample ;
                                            oc:blockType "code_block" ;
                                            oc:codeContent """Price Per Share ($)     Terminal Growth Rate
WACC        1.5%    2.0%    2.5%    3.0%    3.5%
9.0%        $52     $55     $59     $63     $68
9.5%        $48     $51     $54     $58     $62
10.0%       $45     $48     $51     $54     $57
10.5%       $42     $45     $47     $50     $53
11.0%       $40     $42     $44     $47     $50
11.5%       $38     $40     $42     $44     $47
12.0%       $36     $38     $40     $42     $44

Base Case: WACC = 10.8%, g = 2.5% → $46
Format as heatmap: Green (high values) → Yellow → Red (low values)
""" ;
                                            oc:codeLanguage "" ;
                                            oc:contentOrder 3 ;
                                            oc:sourceLocation "lines 245-258" ] ;
                                    oc:sectionLevel 4 ;
                                    oc:sectionOrder 12 ;
                                    oc:sectionTitle "E. DCF Sensitivity Analysis **CRITICAL**" ],
                                [ a oc:Section ;
                                    oc:hasContent [ a oc:CodeExample ;
                                            oc:blockType "code_block" ;
                                            oc:codeContent """Enterprise Value                 $5,069M
- Net Debt (Debt - Cash)         ($450M)
+ Non-operating Assets           $0M
- Minority Interest              $0M
- Preferred Stock                $0M
= Equity Value                   $4,619M

Diluted Shares Outstanding       100M

Price Per Share = $4,619M / 100M = $46.19

Current Stock Price: $42.00
Implied Upside: 10.0%
""" ;
                                            oc:codeLanguage "" ;
                                            oc:contentOrder 1 ;
                                            oc:sourceLocation "lines 224-238" ] ;
                                    oc:sectionLevel 4 ;
                                    oc:sectionOrder 11 ;
                                    oc:sectionTitle "D. Calculate Equity Value and Price Per Share" ],
                                [ a oc:Section ;
                                    oc:hasContent [ a oc:Paragraph ;
                                            oc:blockType "paragraph" ;
                                            oc:contentOrder 3 ;
                                            oc:textContent "**Method 2: Exit Multiple (Alternative)**" ],
                                        [ a oc:Paragraph ;
                                            oc:blockType "paragraph" ;
                                            oc:contentOrder 1 ;
                                            oc:textContent "**Method 1: Perpetuity Growth (Preferred)**" ],
                                        [ a oc:CodeExample ;
                                            oc:blockType "code_block" ;
                                            oc:codeContent """Terminal Value = FCF(2029) × (1 + g) / (WACC - g)

Where:
- FCF(2029) = Final year unlevered FCF from model
- g = Perpetual growth rate (typically 2.0-3.0%)
  - Should not exceed long-term GDP growth
  - Use 2.5% as base case

Example:
FCF(2029) = $500M
g = 2.5%
WACC = 10.8%

Terminal Value = $500M × (1.025) / (0.108 - 0.025)
Terminal Value = $512.5M / 0.083 = $6,175M
""" ;
                                            oc:codeLanguage "" ;
                                            oc:contentOrder 2 ;
                                            oc:sourceLocation "lines 167-183" ],
                                        [ a oc:CodeExample ;
                                            oc:blockType "code_block" ;
                                            oc:codeContent """Terminal Value = EBITDA(2029) × Exit Multiple

Where:
- Exit Multiple = Current peer trading median (e.g., 12-15x EBITDA)

Example:
EBITDA(2029) = $800M
Exit Multiple = 13x

Terminal Value = $800M × 13x = $10,400M
""" ;
